            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Every :terminal has a job-id in the `&channel` read-only option. You can inspect the job's process tree like this:\n\n```\n:echo nvim_get_proc_children(jobpid(&channel))\n:echo nvim_get_proc(jobpid(&channel))\n```",
